# Walkthrough: Squad Shared Tasks & Sprint Goal Fixes

## Changes Made

### Bug 1: Shared Tasks Now Require ALL Squad Members

**Problem:** Selecting 3 people as a squad showed tasks shared by any 2-of-3 as "shared tasks."

**Fix in** [DailyRecapView.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/DailyRecapView.tsx):

```diff
 // Recap mode (line 627)
-taskPersonCounts[taskId].size > 1
+taskPersonCounts[taskId].size === selectedPersonsFilter.size

 // Squad todo mode (line 982)
-persons.size >= 2
+persons.size >= selectedPersonsFilter.size
```

---

### Bug 2: Flexible Sprint Goal Met Calculation

**Problem:** Sprint goal was checked with exact `===` match. Tasks that progressed **beyond** their goal (e.g., goal = "Testing", status = "Completed") were not shown as met.

**Fix:** Created [hasMetSprintGoal()](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/lib/utils.ts) that uses `WORKFLOW_STATUSES` index ordering — `currentIndex >= goalIndex` means met.

Applied in 5 files:
- [utils.ts](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/lib/utils.ts) — new helper function
- [api.ts](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/lib/api.ts) — timeline segment `isCompleted`
- [TaskOverview.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/TaskOverview.tsx) — sorting, stats, display
- [DailyMeetingView.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/DailyMeetingView.tsx) — [DraggableTaskCard](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/DailyMeetingView.tsx#511-700) + [SquadsView](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/DailyMeetingView.tsx#2004-2542)
- [workflow-engine.ts](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/lib/workflow-engine.ts) — staleness check

